1. *Baš* pored kuće se nalazi malo dvorište. (Right next to the house there is a small yard.)
2. Upravo *baš* u tom trenutku je zvonilo. (It was ringing just at that moment.)
3. Ovo je *baš* pravi čaj za ovu hladnu večer. (This is just the right tea for this cold evening.)
4. *Baš* ti se dopada ova majica? (Do you really like this shirt?)
5. *Baš* mi se sviđa kako ona peva. (I really like how she sings.)